{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you pass a spy agency's interview?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Agent of Veil is a 3D puzzle adventure game where the VEIL agency has selected you as a potential recruit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To uncover the agency's secrets, you must first face their many tests, answer interview questions, find clues, and solve hidden puzzles and mysteries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520570/extras/puzzles.gif?t=1739986105\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ghost, Veil's trusted assistant, has meticulously planned the testing ground for their new agent. To succeed in your interview you must answer Ghost's questions, unlock new rooms and areas, solve puzzles, and find clues.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Once you have proven yourself you may peek behind the veil and uncover some of Veil's own secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520570/extras/about_veilUncover.png?t=1739986105\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn about your new spy identity and codename as well as your new colleagues. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520570/extras/about_coll.png?t=1739986105\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">colorful design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">over 100 unique puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">hint system </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">isometric view for easy travel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">spy score and codename </p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3520570?t=1739986105","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520570/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739986105","